  "description": {
    "zh": "别来无恙啊，老兄！快请进！我给你揽了个活儿。储备站里有好几个军营，而且每个军营里通常都会有军械库和储藏室。我想知道那里还有没有东西留下，还是说已经被搬空了。要不要去那边溜达溜达，顺便帮我看看？我这有一个清单，上面有可能留有物资的地方，去这些地方找找。",
    "en": "Salam, brother! Come in! Got a task for you. The reserve base's got several soldier barracks, and usually, they're supposed to have an arsenal and a storage room in them. I wanna know if there's anything left there so I could gather a group for it, or if everything's already looted. Wanna stroll there and check it out? Need to search some specific places, I've even got a list of where there could still be unlooted stuff."
  },
